trans-unit.resname: Sorry, we don't know how to handle that command.
trans-unit.source: Sorry, we don't know how to handle that command.
trans-unit.target: Pardon, tenhle příkaz zpracovat neumíme.

trans-unit.resname: You must provide the mode to change to, either '{mode1}' or '{mode2}'
trans-unit.source: You must provide the mode to change to, either '{mode1}' or '{mode2}'
trans-unit.target: Musíte zadat mód, na který se má bot přepnout, buď ''{mode1}'', nebo ''{mode2}''

trans-unit.resname: The mode was already set to '{mode}'
trans-unit.source: The mode was already set to '{mode}'
trans-unit.target: Režim už byl nastaven na ''{mode}''

trans-unit.resname: The response mode has been changed by {user}.
trans-unit.source: The response mode has been changed by {user}.
trans-unit.target: Režim odpovědi byl změněn uživatelem {user}.

trans-unit.resname: I will now respond to all messages.
trans-unit.source: I will now respond to all messages.
trans-unit.target: Nyní budu odpovídat na všechny zprávy.

trans-unit.resname: I will now only respond to direct @ mentions and threads I'm already mentioned in.
trans-unit.source: I will now only respond to direct @ mentions and threads I'm already mentioned in.
trans-unit.target: Nyní budu odpovídat pouze na přímé @ zmínky a ve vláknech, jichž už jsem součástí.

trans-unit.resname: You must provide the mode to change to, either '{mode1}' or '{mode2}'. The current mode is '{currentMode}'.
trans-unit.source: You must provide the mode to change to, either '{mode1}' or '{mode2}'. The current mode is '{currentMode}'.
trans-unit.target: Musíte uvést režím, buď ''{mode1}'', nebo ''{mode2}''. Součásný režím je ''{currentMode}''.

trans-unit.resname: Hi there!
trans-unit.source: Hi there!
trans-unit.target: Zdravíčko!

trans-unit.resname: I'll respond to your messages if you mention me. You can also configure me to respond to every message in this channel by using the slash command '{command}'
trans-unit.source: I'll respond to your messages if you mention me. You can also configure me to respond to every message in this channel by using the slash command '{command}'
trans-unit.target: Budu odpovídat na vaše dotazy, pokud mě zmíníte. Můžete mě taky nastavit, abych odpovídal na všechny zprávy v tomto kanálu pomocí příkazu ''{command}'

trans-unit.resname: I'll respond to all your messages in this channel. You can also configure me to respond only to direct mentions by using the slash command '{command}'
trans-unit.source: I'll respond to all your messages in this channel. You can also configure me to respond only to direct mentions by using the slash command '{command}'
trans-unit.target: Budu odpovídat na všechny zprávy v tomto kanálu. Můžete mě taky nastavit, abych odpovídal jen, když mě ve zprávě zmíníte, pomocí příkazu ''{command}''

trans-unit.resname: Invalid argument '{argument}', it must be '{mode1}' or '{mode2}'
trans-unit.source: Invalid argument '{argument}', it must be '{mode1}' or '{mode2}'
trans-unit.target: Neplátná možnost ''{argument}'', musí být buď ''{mode1}'', nebo ''{mode2}''

trans-unit.resname: The global limit for messages per day has been reached, I sadly won't be responding to any more messages.
trans-unit.source: The global limit for messages per day has been reached, I sadly won't be responding to any more messages.
trans-unit.target: Byl překročen celkový limit pro počet zpráv za den, na další zprávy bohužel nebudu odpovídat.

trans-unit.resname: You have reached the daily limit of messages for your account, I sadly won't be responding to any more messages from you.
trans-unit.source: You have reached the daily limit of messages for your account, I sadly won't be responding to any more messages from you.
trans-unit.target: Dosáhli jste denního limitu zpráv pro váš účet, bohužel už na vaše zprávy odpovídat nebudu.

trans-unit.resname: The api key you provided is not valid.
trans-unit.source: The api key you provided is not valid.
trans-unit.target: Zadaný api klíč není platný.

trans-unit.resname: Your api key has been successfully saved and usage limits won't apply to you anymore. To delete it run: {command} remove
trans-unit.source: Your api key has been successfully saved and usage limits won't apply to you anymore. To delete it run: {command} remove
trans-unit.target: Váš api klíč byl úspěšně uložen a limity pro používání se na vás již nevztahují. Pro jeho smazání použijte: {command} remove

trans-unit.resname: Your custom api key has been removed.
trans-unit.source: Your custom api key has been removed.
trans-unit.target: Váš vlastní api klíč byl odstraněn.

trans-unit.resname: Sadly ChatGPT didn't reply in time, maybe their servers are too busy?
trans-unit.source: Sadly ChatGPT didn't reply in time, maybe their servers are too busy?
trans-unit.target: ChatGPT bohužel neodpověděl včas, možná jsou jejich servery příliš zaneprázdněné?

trans-unit.resname: Do you want to try again?
trans-unit.source: Do you want to try again?
trans-unit.target: Chcete to zkusit znovu?

trans-unit.source: Yes
trans-unit.target: Ano

trans-unit.source: No
trans-unit.target: Ne

trans-unit.resname: Ok, I won't retry sending the message.
trans-unit.source: Ok, I won't retry sending the message.
trans-unit.target: Dobře, zprávu znovu posílat nebudu.

trans-unit.resname: Ok, I'll retry sending the message.
trans-unit.source: Ok, I'll retry sending the message.
trans-unit.target: Dobře, pošlu zprávu znovu.

trans-unit.resname: Your message has been sent again!
trans-unit.source: Your message has been sent again!
trans-unit.target: Vaše zpráva byla znovu odeslána!
